# Web3Forms — handles form submissions and forwards them to the configured email.
#
# Setup (one-time, ~2 minutes):
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com
# 2. Enter the email address that should receive form submissions
# 3. Confirm the email link, copy the access key
# 4. Paste it as the value below — and as an env var on Vercel (Production + Preview)
#
# This key is intentionally exposed to the browser. It only authorizes form
# submissions to land in the inbox you configured. Rotate it from the Web3Forms
# dashboard if it ever gets abused.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
